    "Name": "Hercules",
    "Details": "The Hercules HRC-LS-9000 carries a wide variety of weapons. For long-range firepower, the 'Mech is armed with a ER PPC. The ER PPC is backed up at intermediate ranges by an LB-X Autocannon/10 that can fire both standard and cluster rounds, making it effective against a wide range of combat units. For close-range combat, the Hercules carries a Streak SRM-2 launcher, an Medium Pulse Laser, and two Small Pulse Lasers. For added protection from missile attacks, the 'Mech also carried an anti-missile system.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Stable Weapons</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.1</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Lower</color>",
